metadata.description:
hey :)

so i'm going to be doing a little series on here - its a series of lofi instrumentals i've been working on, theres 5 in total. 

I'm going to drop one every week, and then on the 6th week drop a mixtape with all of them together + a bonus song and the mixtape with the bonus song is going to be a free presale for all of my collectors :)

all of these songs were made with live instruments, primarily my fender rhodes + guitars / bass. 

a lot of love was put into these i hope you like them <3
metadata.name: Passing By #1
